data.description: 810 NW 21st Ct, a cozy and welcoming home situated in a friendly Miami neighborhood. The home features a spacious and inviting layout, perfect for both relaxation and entertaining. With ample natural light, modern amenities, and a serene outdoor space, this property also has a studio. Its location is conveniently close to local shops, schools, and parks. Operations as an Airbnb, seller added 2nd unit without permits. Buyer must assume active violation.
